For an ideal gas, for isothermal reversible process,
$$
\begin{aligned}
& \Delta S=2.303 \mathrm{nR} \log \left(\frac{\mathrm{v}_2}{\mathrm{v}_1}\right) \\
& =2.303 \times 2 \times 8.314 \times \log \left(\frac{100}{10}\right) \\
& =38.3 \mathrm{~J} \mathrm{~mol}^{-1} \cdot \mathrm{k}^{-1}
\end{aligned}
$$
